commit 416f16dd9f93b6465882826b018e16917b34e537
Author: Dan Roundhill <dan@automattic.com>
Date:   Fri Jan 2 12:50:37 2015 -0800

    Fixes janky list reload when a Simperium change is received:
    
     * Moved `NoteBlockAdapter` into its own class
     * `NotificationDetailListFragment` now has a private instance of `NoteBlockAdapter`, so it can just update the backing array instead of recreating the adapter every time we reload the list.
     * `NoteBlockAdapter` overrides `hasStableIds`, which helps prevent rows from reloading their content unnecessarily.

