commit 88368deadbe3ce6fc50fd0a8d0896d99b6191c9c
Author: Dan Roundhill <dan@automattic.com>
Date:   Tue Sep 9 11:50:59 2014 -0700

    Comments/Notifications activities upgraded to use 'undo bar'.
    
     * CommentsActivity and NotificationsActivity now handle the moderation/reply actions instead of `CommentDetailFragment`.
     * Moderating a comment will dismiss `CommentDetailFragment` and show the undo bar for destructive actions.
     * Undo basically hides the comment that's being moderated until after the undo bar disappears, then the request is made. Tapping undo 'unhides' the comment/notification.
     * `NotificationsActivity` and `CommentsActivity` have both had the tablet landscape dual-pane mode removed.

