commit 27008fd52f39ac13234f7736ef21f8ad3b68b6dd
Author: Beau Collins <beaucollins@gmail.com>
Date:   Fri Nov 15 19:34:43 2013 -0800

    Note managed by Simperium
    
    Switches the Note to be completely managed by default Simperium stack. This
    means any note stored in the current DB will be abandoned and left in the old
    DB.
    
    This works since Notes are treated as transient data. Using your own datastore
    is something Simperium needs to handle better.

