    fix #48: notification refresh
    * Store notification cache in sqlite
    * Fetch new notifications when a push is received
    * Broadcast a "refresh-me-please" message when a push is received so NotificationsActivity is refreshed if it's running and a push is received
    * read and unzip full_note_data in payload if exists and add it to the notification cache (props to @daniloercoli for idea and code)
    * if full_note_data is not in the payload, a temporary placeholder is created. Placeholders are deleted when notifications are refreshed with a REST call.

