commit 3b59223aae9b069adcd0f48dd7ff4b0f9208a9ef
Author: Beau Collins <beaucollins@gmail.com>
Date:   Wed Apr 3 11:00:59 2013 -0700

    Setting up project with example and test projects
    
    The android project under `examples/note-reader` will be used as the application
    under test. The initial test project is located at `examples/note-reader/test`.
    
    To run tests, connect a device or emulator and run `ant debug install test` from
    the test project directory.
    
    custom_rules.xml provides some additional ant tasks for managing the library:
    
    - `ant download-libs` will install the `android-async-http` jar file in `libs`
    - `ant package` will compile to jar files, one including android-async and one
      without it and place them in `dist/`

